transform_def.name: designed34
transform_def.string: let r = 1 / length(p_in) s = cos(p_in.x / (sin(abs(p_in.y) * abs(sin(p_in.y)) + abs(p_in.x * sin(length(p_in)))))) t = tan(length(p_in) + abs(sin(p_in.x * (tan(p_in.y / length(p_in)))))) * (s / fourpi()) z = tan(lerp(s, t, 0.25) * (r * halfpi())) con1 = abs(z) < r con2 = abs(z) > r in (if if fill > 0.0 then con1 else con2 then p_in else vec2(0.0)) * weight
